{"tid":2368143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國再因香港問題制裁6人，蓬佩奧稱續追究責任","createTime":"2021-01-16T02:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T03:17:11.000Z","uid":278587,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1611885a1c2bf5f55818245ad85bee3ff9e6b772","tid":2368143,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/138168529_4197392380368786_8438121191207289019_o.png?_nc_cat=103&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=2LMZDXUnLEQAX-ONLxH&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=30&amp;oh=e31af0853be02be52edc1469f1f464a8&amp;oe=602806CF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp526x296%2F138168529_4197392380368786_8438121191207289019_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D2LMZDXUnLEQAX-ONLxH%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D30%26oh%3De31af0853be02be52edc1469f1f464a8%26oe%3D602806CF&h=a44dc74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部在香港警方大規模拘捕民主派人士後，再向6人實施制裁，包括中共中央統戰部部長尤權、中央駐港維護國安公署副署長孫青野、全國人大常委譚耀宗、警務處國安處處長蔡展鵬、負責國家安全的警務處助理處長簡啟恩和江學禮，他們在美國的資產將會被凍結。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，香港當局的行動，是表明香港自由與民主進程遭受中共根本破壞的又一例子，被制裁的人有份制定、通過或實施港區國安法。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧敦促北京與香港當局，立即釋放只是出於行使基本法與中英聯合聲明所承諾之權利與自由，而被國安法或其他法律針對的人，並撤銷對他們的檢控，美方會繼續動用所有可行工具追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570706-20210116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570706-20210116.htm&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=77689177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570706-20210116.htm&h=3d53263f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570706-20210116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ec2bb72fb2390044a829f61df908219f1a74e935","tid":2368143,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"大力d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900e52a8539894b7e3a897348909d6cd70489dd0","tid":2368143,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"出得地圖炮未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd1c1ccb399959432d522afeee2002f63779f62","tid":2368143,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"侵侵連任左一定大大力報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a49a7c51ba731f312d085781216b0d6d71f139","tid":2368143,"uid":371815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"剩返四日天蓬大元師都chur 盡去搞中共同港共真係唔話得，希望佢可以成功當選2024嘅美國總統"},{"pid":"b776c6ad395b6f90bcd503798ed87af3be861a80","tid":2368143,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"d8fafd0e96fad0771276efc73a70f2de13f08278","tid":2368143,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"比卡超腳震未？"},{"pid":"a84c74a7e8ac3823c0b20f5681f62a0d2ce8c585","tid":2368143,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"Pompeo, 多謝你"},{"pid":"dd1daed37ff707d327810c3109e7236ec00f22b1","tid":2368143,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb07b03734cb30e72634ac341824db9ce8f7792","tid":2368143,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}